EN: His true nature hidden beneath the surface is good-hearted.

ZH: 她毫不掩饰她的本性。
EN: She doesn't hide her nature at all.

ZH: 虽然他看起来粗鲁，但他的本性是友善的。
EN: Although he may seem rough, his nature is actually friendly.

